The paper also mentions the use of autoregressive MADE networks, which are commonly used in deep learning for time series analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of neural networks and deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in the sub-categories cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
